&lt;br&gt;Can you remember
nothing?&lt;br&gt;- It wasn't me.

00:10:08.200 --> 00:10:11.280
&lt;br&gt;Are you sure?&lt;br&gt;- I am no murderer.

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:19.960
&lt;br&gt;Who did it?&lt;br&gt;- Schrämli.

