&lt;br&gt;The man or the dog?&lt;br&gt;- Both.

00:10:25.960 --> 00:10:28.880
&lt;br&gt;Do you meet strangers in your sleep?

00:10:28.960 --> 00:10:32.560
&lt;br&gt;I don't know the
