&lt;br&gt;The dead man
photographed me, &lt;br&gt;but why?

00:10:37.040 --> 00:10:40.080
&lt;br&gt;Are you perhaps
famous?&lt;br&gt;- Not that I know of.

00:10:40.160 --> 00:10:42.720
&lt;br&gt;You don't seem to
know&lt;br&gt;much about yourself.

00:10:42.800 --> 00:10:44.960
&lt;br&gt;Find out.

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:54.160
&lt;br&gt;And close up here again!

