protect from the world.)

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:08.200
(Perhaps both.)

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:14.480
(But first I wanted to find out
more about this sleepwalking.)

00:11:21.560 --> 00:11:23.960
The best sleep
researcher in town.

00:11:24.040 --> 00:11:26.040
And how do you sleep?

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:28.760
Mostly horizontally
under my desk.

00:11:28.840 --> 00:11:32.360
Excessive caffeine or alcohol consumption?
- If possible, yes.

00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:35.480
How do you feel each time
before falling asleep?- Tired.

00:11:37.280 --> 00:11:39.280
Please take the questions seriously.

00:11:41.480 --> 00:11:44.640
The reason for my sleep
disorder is a woman.- Interesting.

00:11:44.720 --> 00:11:47.800
We met at a self-help group for people

00:11:47.880 --> 00:11:51.440
with sleep problems .- Very interesting.

00:11:51.520 --> 00:11:53.960
Is it possible, that one could hurt someone as a sleepwalker?

00:11:54.040 --> 00:11:56.560
- Very, very interesting.

