00:17:02.360 --> 00:17:06.119
Yes, winter is coming.
So, uhm, soon.

00:17:06.200 --> 00:17:09.200
So, not so soon either.

00:17:09.280 --> 00:17:11.280
Also, he was just here.

00:17:15.480 --> 00:17:19.119
I've been thinking about
what you said last night.

00:17:20.480 --> 00:17:24.960
And I think, if I could,
then I would go to Sweden.

00:17:26.079 --> 00:17:28.200
It's always dark there in the winter.

00:17:28.280 --> 00:17:31.360
Then I could just sit
outside with you and ...

00:17:31.440 --> 00:17:35.120
What kind of person are you?
