- No.

00:20:09.280 --> 00:20:11.800
Come Chnurrli, let's go!

00:20:14.520 --> 00:20:16.720
I am against violence. Mostly.

00:20:16.800 --> 00:20:18.800
Actually always.

00:20:20.480 --> 00:20:22.480
Come Wuffgang, let's go.

00:20:24.240 --> 00:20:25.240
* Whining

00:20:25.480 --> 00:20:26.480
